        <h1>Some rules</h1>
        <h4>1) Survey<br></h4>
        <p>1. You can not change question number on non existing number</p>
        <p>2. If you add question description and does not set it at least 2 answers this question will be deleted</p>
        <p>3. If you try to add the same answer it will not be added</p>
        <p>4. For submitting the question it should contain 1 right answer and at least 1 wrong answer (question can contain 10 answers)</p>
        <p>5. You can edit answers by clicking the number of question in questions list</p>
        <h4>2) Questionnaire</h4>
        <p>1. Pay attention, if you choose 10-point scale, you will not be able to change it on 5-point scale</p>
        <p>2. If you try to add the same question it will not be added</p>
        <p>3. If you delete one of the descriptions, all grades will be added equally to the nearest descriptions in the table</p>
        <p>4. If you edit description scale, you take grades from other the nearest in the table descriptions (if description is first</p>
        <p>in list, 1-st range will be frozen, if description is last and grades are available, you can add all remaining grades)</p>
